---
import DisplayCards from './DisplayCards';
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative accent -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-sand to-transparent"></div>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <div class="reveal max-w-2xl">
      <span class="font-body text-xs font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-terracotta">
        <span data-lang-en>Who I am</span>
        <span data-lang-es>Quién soy</span>
      </span>
      <h2 class="mt-3 font-heading font-bold text-navy leading-tight" style="font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw + 0.5rem, 3rem);">
        <span data-lang-en>
          Consumer psychology runs deep.<br />
          <span class="text-slate/70">Everything else runs wide.</span>
        </span>
        <span data-lang-es>
          La psicología del consumidor es mi profundidad.<br />
          <span class="text-slate/70">Todo lo demás es mi alcance.</span>
        </span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
      <!-- Bio text with headshot -->
      <div class="reveal space-y-5" style="transition-delay: 100ms;">
        <!-- Headshot -->
        <div class="mb-8">
          <div class="relative inline-block">
            <img
              src="/images/profile/headshot.jpg"
              alt="Juan Minoprio — Marketing Specialist"
              class="w-48 md:w-64 rounded-xl"
              loading="eager"
              width="400"
              height="400"
            />
            <div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 w-full h-full rounded-xl border-2 border-terracotta/20 -z-10"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div data-lang-en>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed">
            I'm fascinated by why people buy — the behavioral triggers, the brand associations, the invisible forces that drive every decision. That fascination isn't academic. I apply it every day at Charles Schwab, where I build campaigns that reach millions of investors and advisors.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed mt-5">
            My expertise runs deep in consumer psychology and wide across AI for marketing, data storytelling, product marketing, and MarTech. Before Schwab, I spent 3+ years in Miami's agency world running paid media, content strategy, and influencer programs.
          </p>
          <p class="font-accent italic text-lg text-navy/70 mt-5">
            Bilingual (English/Spanish). Miami-raised, FIU alum. Building at the intersection of behavioral science, marketing strategy, and AI.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div data-lang-es>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed">
            Me fascina entender por qué la gente compra — los disparadores conductuales, las asociaciones de marca, las fuerzas invisibles que impulsan cada decisión. Esa fascinación no es académica. La aplico todos los días en Charles Schwab, donde construyo campañas que llegan a millones de inversores y asesores.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed mt-5">
            Mi experiencia es profunda en psicología del consumidor y amplia en IA para marketing, storytelling de datos, product marketing y MarTech. Antes de Schwab, pasé más de 3 años en el mundo de agencias de Miami manejando paid media, estrategia de contenido y programas de influencers.
          </p>
          <p class="font-accent italic text-lg text-navy/70 mt-5">
            Bilingüe (inglés/español). Criado en Miami, egresado de FIU. Construyendo en la intersección de ciencia del comportamiento, estrategia de marketing e IA.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Display Cards — Interactive pillar showcase -->
      <div class="reveal flex items-center justify-center py-8" style="transition-delay: 200ms;">
        <DisplayCards client:only="react" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
